    { "@type": "HowToStep", "position": 2, "name": "Write answer capsules after every heading", "text": "After every H2 and H3, write a 40-60 word self-contained factual block that directly answers the heading. Over 90% of AI Overview citations pull from answer capsules. Lead with the answer, then elaborate." },
